WEBVTT

00:00:00.538 --> 00:00:03.207
I wrote this journal entry in 2013.

00:00:06.961 --> 00:00:09.756
"I've been sleeping restlessly for months.

00:00:10.631 --> 00:00:13.676
There's a constant feeling
of tension in my body.

00:00:15.303 --> 00:00:18.139
I love ministry as a Catholic priest,

00:00:18.181 --> 00:00:20.516
the opportunity to share
my faith with people

00:00:20.516 --> 00:00:23.394
and support them as we journey
through life together.

00:00:24.729 --> 00:00:27.732
But I have a desire to share my life
with another person.

00:00:29.567 --> 00:00:31.611
I knew, in discerning ministry,